window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>This title will be streaming in Audible Plus through September 1st, 2021. </b></p> <p>Lindon has a year left. </p> <p>When his time runs out, he’ll have to fight an opponent that no one believes he can beat. Unless he learns sacred arts the right way, from scratch, he won’t have a chance to win...and even then, the odds are against him. </p> <p>In the course of their training, he and Yerin travel to the Blackflame Empire, where they fight to master an ancient power left behind by a fallen clan. This is Lindon’s chance to learn a true Path, but there are those who do not wish to see these lost techniques revived. </p> <p>Success means a chance at life, but failure means death. </p> <p>In the sacred arts, those who risk the most travel the farthest. </p>"; 
